project.name: CodeEditorWithinACodeEditor
project.notes: This project is a small, JS code editor within Snap! It was created for the Berkeley Computer Science Academy (Summer 2024). I developed this with the base from "Code Editor" by joecooldoo: https://snap.berkeley.edu/project?username=joecooldoo&projectname=Code%20Editor When using this project, make sure javascript extensions are enabled, otherwise this project will not work, and you will be left with an annoying error. To view the output of your code, go to the devloper window and look at the console. Currently, there is an issue with using braces, and I will be working to resolve it. Please, do not abuse this project, and I can not be held accountable for any damage caused by the javascript capabilities this project has.
